<component name="NrrdPad" category="Filters">
  <overview>
    <authors>
      <author>David Weinstein</author>
      <author>Martin Cole</author>
    </authors>
    <summary>Pad the size of a nrrd along its axes.</summary>
    <description>
      <p>The user interface for NrrdPad varies depending upon the
dimenion of the input nrrd.  For each axis (except the Tuple Axis),
the user inputs the amount to prepend and append to the axis.  NrrdPad
outputs a new NrrdData of the specified size.</p>
    </description>
    <examplesr>Teem/nets/test/pad.net</examplesr>
  </overview>
  <io>
    <inputs lastportdynamic="no">
      <port>
        <name>Nrrd</name>
	<datatype>Teem::Nrrd</datatype>
      </port>
    </inputs>
    <outputs>
      <port>
        <name>Nrrd</name>
	<datatype>Teem::Nrrd</datatype>
      </port>
    </outputs>
  </io>
  <testing>
  </testing>
</component>
